{"tid":1296680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港首女性考獲遠洋船輪機長資格  曾被同事視為臥底","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:54:26.000Z","uid":28366,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9e875788fcecc92da7df5ba380f9ce7b348908","tid":1296680,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190708/_2019070817393075400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190708%2F_2019070817393075400.jpg&h=a48c43c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">郭詠恩成為本港首名考獲遠洋船輪機長資格的女高級船員。</span><br />\n<br />\n航運界一直鮮有女性踏足，現年32歲的郭詠恩打破局限，成為本港首名考獲遠洋船輪機長資格的女高級船員。郭詠恩透露，每次行船，船上大多船員都是男性，會認為女性不能勝任船員工作，但只要展現出女性的才能，必定可獲對方認同。<br />\n<br />\n郭詠恩11年前修畢香港專業教育學院的機械工程學高級文憑後，了解自己經常「坐唔定」，決定投身挑戰性大的航運業。她一步步為夢想邁進，加入了中英船舶管理公司至今，先從見習管輪起步，慢慢升至管理層的大管輪，即輪機（機艙）部門的「第二把交椅」，負責管理下屬的工作，在機房中負責檢查及修理船的機器。<br />\n<br />\n但是，她並未為此停步，在海上闖蕩數年，歷盡嚴寒及酷熱的天氣，她仍決心繼續她的航海夢。約3年前她開始下決心獲遠洋船輪機長資格，曾經失敗3次，經過她的努力不懈，最後今年成功濟身於一個傳統以男性為主的行業，並成為本港首名考獲遠洋船輪機長資格的女高級船員。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「行船跑馬三分險」，少有女性願意加入航運業。郭詠恩指，其公司的船員大多以印度人為主，她在船上經常是唯一的女性及唯一的香港人。她笑言，有不少同事暗地裏指她是來自其他地方的臥底，因為女性太少見。<br />\n<br />\n外界總認為男性擔任船員，總比女性好。郭詠恩坦言，船上大多船員都是男性，認為女船員難以升任工作，但她強調，只要展示女性的才能及能力，一定可以得到認同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190708/_2019070817393112792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190708%2F_2019070817393112792.jpg&h=baad2006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3006750/org/396c06564bcde01d90152c39663f7ae1.jpg/phXtgOX1TX7d3ounI6syYsXi385CXpLUHdW6XB3Vulw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3006750%2Forg%2F396c06564bcde01d90152c39663f7ae1.jpg%2FphXtgOX1TX7d3ounI6syYsXi385CXpLUHdW6XB3Vulw&h=faa2cc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/459360/org/d085c05a7d0fb14c2e4979406b2d16b9.JPG/O8qKxP96QQM1chmnSOWHDGqI9tqNbQHBAnKBPgJygT4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F459360%2Forg%2Fd085c05a7d0fb14c2e4979406b2d16b9.JPG%2FO8qKxP96QQM1chmnSOWHDGqI9tqNbQHBAnKBPgJygT4&h=7a19c82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ddc3cabf3044bd4078ed8f9bb0d13321cc4fde9","tid":1296680,"uid":7452,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"安全樣"},{"pid":"5a4e1196698024c11ac350a4eb52eb26be46dfb0","tid":1296680,"uid":65201,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"有閪既行船都可以出篇訪問，呢d就係男女平等"},{"pid":"b88ca610ff4d9343cc73b21da423f27a8a79b1c0","tid":1296680,"uid":1255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2ddc3cabf3044bd4078ed8f9bb0d13321cc4fde9","tid":1296680,"uid":7452,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"安全樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"你真係天撚真"},{"pid":"374110674e7f48deba44bd5f668d314283c016b0","tid":1296680,"uid":50663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"餓起上黎真係唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"4e98dcb7a0f74abe9e5046f7681a3651f8c40a52","tid":1296680,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"最大粒嗰個位？"},{"pid":"3a59be6cbcb4f5c788acdd511b48717b9823fbe2","tid":1296680,"uid":144883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd30ef8966a3f3187d4fb2b41de5ab326a2df6a0","tid":1296680,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"享受人生🌭🌭🌭🌭🥖🥖🥖💁🏻&zwj;♀️🥕🥕🥕🍆🍆🍆"},{"pid":"6522b359b7dd0ce4bb5b0e0df930c262c688a7d1","tid":1296680,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy